{"tid":2001714,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[國際關係撚］冷戰格局下美國有咩誘因幫香港人？","createTime":"2020-05-04T17:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-06T05:59:06.000Z","uid":205346,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e15054e22a5976698d59763535edc6a758131bba","tid":2001714,"uid":205346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T17:27:06.000Z","msg":"香港係中美博奕嘅一隻棋子<br />\n支那透過香港連接世界 西方國家係香港亦有好多利益<br />\n不過隨住支那武肺爆到西方國家七國咁亂之際<br />\n西方國家圍堵支那嘅冷戰格局已經形成<br />\n<br />\n最近中聯辦越嚟越高調，亦都係反映緊支那寧願放棄香港作為連接世界窗口呢個角色，都要全面控制住香港，防止香港有可能成為令中共政權倒台嘅缺口<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，係冷戰格局下西方國家圍堵支那，去中國化 企業撤華似乎係疫後大趨勢，香港對美國而言仲有幾多利益？有咩誘因會幫到香港抗爭？<br />\n<br />\n我怕香港好快淪為東柏林/ 新疆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"affd2aff7f8f0236f9a6e0b08949099ab0c7055f","tid":2001714,"uid":205346,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T17:29:38.000Z","msg":"延伸閱讀：<br />\n<br />\n練乙錚分析國際「新冷戰」香港角色：中共要手握絕對控制權<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/29306/練乙錚-新冷戰-中美關係-29347/新冷戰\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F29306%2F%E7%B7%B4%E4%B9%99%E9%8C%9A-%E6%96%B0%E5%86%B7%E6%88%B0-%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82-29347%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%B7%E6%88%B0&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1je9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=319c1f3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/29306/練乙錚-新冷戰-中美關係-29347/新冷戰</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後疫情時代，中國對香港的野心<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/opinion/20200428/china-hong-k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fopinion%2F20200428%2Fchina-hong-k&d=QLsQNhMpkN58D9M0TNJg1je9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=abae30de\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/opinion/20200428/china-hong-k</a>"},{"pid":"90eb031a8a55c33626bdb84a68017cca46ad78dd","tid":2001714,"uid":205346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T17:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets